title: #92Noon Live from TCO: Bob Sturm / Matt Birk / Britton Colquitt
description:
The FAN's Paul Allen and Eric Nordquist are live from the TCO Performance Center in Eagan ahead of the big Sunday Night Football game against the Dallas Cowboys!

They discuss PJ Fleck's new contract, the Wild being victorious over the Ducks, mixed in with plenty of Vikings talkers.
